partnerDetails.about: Welcome to Okavango Electrical Wholesalers, Cape Town’s leading independent wholesale supplier of premium branded electrical goods. We supply products to leading property developers, electrical and building contractors, municipalities, retail outlets and the general public, for all industrial, commercial and domestic projects.
